tion for any reason (with a few restrictions being involved on controlled substances).<br>
<br>
If you notice, medications like Claritin, Allegra, and Vioxx are actually marketed for the conditions they are approved for (allergies and osteoarthritis).  Many drugs are marketed this way, but some are not.<br>
<br>
Also, there has been some loosening of restrictions over the last several years regarding exactly what you can and can't say.  Laws used to be more restrictive.<br>
<br>
